title: Eternal Sunshine of The Spotless Mind - encoded for iPod
description:
Description
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

The movie "Eternal Sunshine Of The Spotless Mind" starring Jim Carey and Kate Winslet. Encoded for the iPod with the m4v extension to be more compatible with iTunes. The movie is widescreen without letterbox (no black bars). Your iPod will automatically display it in full frame and your television will add letterbox if it is not a widescreen tv. The video and audio bitrate matches that of apple. I prefer quality over quantity, so my movies are optimized for tv playback.

Video
-------------------------------
Codec/Info : H.264
Codec/CC : avc1 
Bit rate : 1409 Kbps 
Width : 640 pixels 
Height : 344 pixels 
Display Aspect ratio : 16/9 
Frame rate : 23.976 fps 

Audio
-------------------------------

Codec/Info : AAC Low Complexity 
Bit rate : 128 Kbps 
Channel(s) : 2 channels 
Channel positions : L R 
Sampling rate : 48 KHz 
Resolution : 16 bits
